# Trivy allowlist.
#
# Each line is either a Trivy ID (CVE-..., AVD-..., DS-..., KSV-...) or a
# comment. Per ADR-0027 §Negative and docs/ops/dep-management.md §Allowlist,
# each entry MUST be preceded by a comment block with all four fields:
#
#   # owner: @<github-handle>
#   # reason: <why this finding does not apply here>
#   # expires: YYYY-MM-DD (≤90 days from add)
#   <TRIVY-ID>
#
# Trivy reads only the IDs, but the comments are part of the review contract.
#
# (no active entries)
